January 15, 2013 In "Health" Dr Chibawanye Ene, a US-based Nigerian Doctor, has won the 2019 Ronald L. Bittner Award on Brain Tumor Research. May 19, 2019 In "News" Gov. Muhammadu Bindow of Adamawa state has personally intervened in situation involving a doctor in a private clinic in Yola who conducted a surgery on Hamman, a 23-year-old herdsman from Fufore Local Government Area of the state where he removed his kidney after mistaken it for tumour. September 19, 2016 In "News"